.Dd January 5, 2017
.Dt DC_BUFFER_NEW 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm dc_buffer_new
.Nd create an resizable binary buffer
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libdivecomputer
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In libdivecomputer/buffer.h
.Ft "dc_buffer_t *"
.Fo dc_buffer_new
.Fa "size_t capacity"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Create a resizable binary buffer of initial size
.Fa capacity ,
which may be zero.
The created buffer must be freed with
.Xr dc_buffer_free 3 .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
Returns a pointer to a
.Vt dc_buffer_t
or
.Dv NULL
on memory exhaustion.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr dc_buffer_free 3
